{
  "title": "Rich Peppery Brazilian Chicken Skewers",
  "description": "Silky and adventurous Brazilian dish featuring pecan nuts, mushimono-steam, and ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly ingredients, with a rich peppery flavor",
  "cuisine": "Brazilian",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
